abstract: Luís Fabiano Clemente (born 8 November 1980), commonly known as Luís Fabiano, is a Brazilian footballer who plays for São Paulo FC as a striker.Luís Fabiano is a prolific goalscorer and was ranked the highest scoring Brazilian of the 21st century by IFFHS.
